- [http://www.instructables.com/id/Obstacle-Avoiding-Robot-Using-Ultrasonic-With-Eviv/ *Obstacle avoiding robot*] with integrated IMU which helped robot to follow particular path to reach its destination avoiding the inbetween obstacle.
- [http://www.instructables.com/id/Smartphone-Controlled-Electric-Skateboard-With-Evi/ *Smartphone controlled skateboard*] using bluetooth module to control via smartphone and proximity sensor to prevent accidental collision
- *Home automation system* for smart homes with a digital password protected door lock, smartphone controlled home appliances,
and capable of detecting human presence and light up the rooms accordingly
- Various IoT Applications like 
-- [http://www.instructables.com/id/Chatting-Using-evive/ *Chat Bot*] -- chatting with two different evive via WiFi
-- [https://www.hackster.io/evive-team/tweet-using-arduino-esp-and-keypad-a303e9 *Twitter Bot*] -- Tweet to ypur personal Twitter account via evive 
-- [http://www.instructables.com/id/Plant-Monitoring-and-Watering-System-Using-Evive-A/ *Plant Monitoring system*] -- to monitor moisture and temperature of plant environment and water them accordingly
- Made detailed instructions tutorial for these projects as well on [http://www.instructables.com/member/evivetoolkit/ Instructables], [https://www.hackster.io/evive-team Hackster.io] etc.
